title: Inserter/Warehouse Help: This position is part time, on (pic)
text:
Inserter/Warehouse Help: This position is part time, on ad date: 10/22/2015 
Inserter/Warehouse Help: This position is part time, on call, up to 4 nights per week. Approx. 7pm-1am. Physical requirements include lifting 30-75lbs, standing for long periods of time. $9 per hr. No experience necessary, will train the right person. APPLY TODAY: If you are interested in any of these positions at our Smith River Printing Plant please complete an employment application available at our downtown Crescent City office on the corner of 3rd and H St. Also available online at http://my.triplicate.com/apply and can be dropped off at our office Mon-Fri., 8am-5pm with attached resums. EOE / Drug screen required. 707-464-2141 Click image to enlarge
